{
  "text": "To fully pinpoint both the benefits and tradeoffs of Contour, we compare it with several known systems designed to provide transparency. In particular, we consider the tradeoffs as compared to Certificate Transparency (CT), Collective Signing (CoSi) [CITATION_1] , CONIKS [CITATION_2] , and Bitcoin. We summarize these tradeoffs in Table 3 .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "690071",
